NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
A.P., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
J.C., Defendant. In the Matter of A.C. and J.C., Minors-Respondents. C-109 September Term 2018
080975 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 28, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001545-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
